    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About The Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Sea Trip</strong> is 2D RPG deep water adventure game.  The Oceans have many dangers,  but there are new dangers that threaten all deep sea and ocean life.  You are The Fish and must save the day by helping ocean friends, defeating toxic and trash monsters while figuring out their way through the ocean and life.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Winner of the Best Innovation Award at 2DCon 2025!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208050/extras/3fa332ada32c8c8ab038b1b4d2293ba2.avif?t=1770322190\" width=378 height=334 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Featuring:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic roleplaying elements mixed with modern themes </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of enemies to defeat with various battle styles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208050/extras/db322b7f03683fdf383d4046210fbe2c.poster.avif?t=1770322190\" width=1170 height=652 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208050/extras/db322b7f03683fdf383d4046210fbe2c.webm?t=1770322190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2208050/extras/db322b7f03683fdf383d4046210fbe2c.mp4?t=1770322190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buildings and caves to explore</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span cla